  "description": "Aquatic Chain showcase: OPAL's granular clouds pre-diffused by Fathom's character morph at 0.25 (slightly bright emphasis helps the grain peaks cut through). Drift at 5 voices with high diffusion turns the granular scatter into a shimmering ensemble. Reef at size 0.7 and high density wraps the grains in an FDN reverb so dense it sounds like looking up through water at scattered light. Tide off — the grains already move.",
